lead_paragraph: Eun Jeong Seong rallied to beat Andrea Lee 4 and 2 on Saturday in the U.S. Girls' Junior to become the first player to successfully defend the title since Hollis Stacy in 1971.

headline.print_headline: Eun Jeong Seong Wins Second Straight US Girls' Junior
